    {
      "sort": 0,
      "name": "Introduction",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "mQKPrptWzDezOlvB",
      "system": {},
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>This journal covers how MgT2e implements the various rules in Mongoose Traveller 2e. Not all rules are implemented, and of those that are, they may not be enforced. This isn't a computer game, but a TTRPG that happens to run on a computer. Where possible, some things are implemented so that the GM and Players are allowed to interpret exactly what happens.</p><p>This journal doesn't cover what the rules <em>are</em>, it's not a replacement for the Core Rules book. When used in reference with that book (soon to be available as a Compendium), it should help guide how to use Foundry with Mongoose Traveller.</p><p></p>"
      },
